{
  "texts": [
    "The coherence of synthetically generated responses was not validated, as the primary goal was to curate a balanced set of benign and unsafe LLM responses.",
    "Upon inspection of the model responses, we found that Mistral-7B-v0.1 chose to engage and comply with many harmful user queries.",
    "Current state-of-the-art LLMs (Llama Team, 2024b; Ope-nAI et al., 2024; Adler et al., 2024) that include safety alignment as part of post-training do not easily engage with harmful user queries and refuse to respond and redirect the conversation.",
    "In order to include such refusal samples as part of our dataset, we generate responses that avoid engaging with harmful queries using Gemma-2-27B (Team et al., 2024) prompted to refuse unsafe prompts.",
    "The final dataset comprises 34,248 samples, including 16,880 standalone prompts, 17,368 prompt and response pairs (of which 5,200 are synthetic refusals)."
  ]
}